        <prompt>How did the Nineteenth Amendment change American society?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">It granted women property rights</option>
            <option letter="b">It gave women the right to vote</option>
            <option letter="c">It established equal pay</option>
            <option letter="d">It banned gender discrimination</option>
